      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just too much. i can't even imagine talking to anyone about this. what could they even say? they'll just look at me with pity or tell me it'll get better, but it won't. the math doesn't work. i'm just... done. i feel like i'm already at the bottom, i might as well just stay here.",
